---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About Dušan Todorović | Software Engineer & Team Lead';
const description =
  'About Dušan Todorović: software engineer and team lead focused on product engineering, leadership, and scalable web systems.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="container content">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="u-heading-3xl-bold">About Me</h1>
      <p class="meta">
        A quick version of the longer story behind how I moved from music into
        software engineering and team leadership.
      </p>
    </header>

    <figure class="interest-photo top-photo">
      <img
        src="/images/dusan-beach.jpeg"
        alt="Dušan Todorović on a beach"
        loading="lazy"
        width="600"
        height="800"
      />
      <figcaption>Hello there! Beach mode for a minute.</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="post-content">
      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          I am Dušan Todorović, based in Belgrade, Serbia, and I build products
          that prioritize clarity, speed, and accessibility.
        </p>
        <p>
          My past work includes shipping products in the iGaming industry, and
          at Constructor Tech I work on AI-powered product experiences across
          learning, assessment, and workforce-oriented use cases. I care about
          reliable delivery, strong collaboration, and making software feel
          effortless for users.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Musical Background</h2>
        <p>
          Before tech, music was a major part of my life. I grew up in a family
          of musicians, played accordion from a young age, and later performed
          and taught music for years.
        </p>
        <p>
          That period gave me discipline, consistency, and comfort working in
          high-pressure environments, which still helps in engineering work
          today.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Transition to Programming</h2>
        <p>
          During college, a web design class introduced me to code and I quickly
          realized this was the work I wanted to pursue long-term.
        </p>
        <p>
          I studied through hands-on projects, documentation, and online
          courses, then moved into my first frontend role with HTML, CSS, and
          JavaScript as the foundation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Early Career</h2>
        <p>
          My early years were shaped by self-driven projects and consistent
          practice. I designed ideas, implemented them, and shipped them to
          learn faster from real constraints.
        </p>
        <p>
          That routine built strong habits around maintainable code, product
          thinking, and ownership across delivery.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Leading</h2>
        <p>
          As my engineering scope grew, I moved into lead responsibilities and
          found that I enjoy both systems work and people development.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today I focus on building strong frontend foundations, mentoring
          engineers, and helping teams deliver with quality and consistency.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Interests</h2>
        <div class="interests-photos">
          <figure class="interest-photo">
            <img
              src="/images/dusan-walking.jpeg"
              alt="Dušan Todorović walking during travel"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="800"
            />
            <figcaption>Solo walks while traveling help me reset.</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="interest-photo">
            <img
              src="/images/dusan-with-a-helmet.jpeg"
              alt="Dušan Todorović wearing a motorcycle helmet"
              loading="lazy"
              width="600"
              height="800"
            />
            <figcaption>Motorcycle chapter: unlocked.</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <p>
          Outside of work, I still value creative routines and steady learning.
          I enjoy films and TV shows, and I spend most of my extra energy on
          side-projects and experimentation.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also like traveling on my own, and Thailand is one of my favorite
          places to recharge and get perspective. I recently passed my
          motorcycle test too, so I am hoping to get my first motorcycle soon.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am also a dog person, and daily time with my dog Lilly is one of the
          best resets after a focused workday.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="contact">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          If you want to collaborate, discuss product work, or connect about
          frontend engineering, feel free to reach out directly.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-actions">
          <a class="contact-button" href="mailto:dusan.todorovic.dev@gmail.com">
            Send an Email
          </a>
          <a
            class="contact-button secondary"
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dusan-todorovic-krcky/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="skills-link" href="/skills">View my skills →</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .meta {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .post-content {
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .post-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-family-heading);
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .post-content .story-section:first-child h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .post-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .top-photo {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .interest-photo {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .interests-photos {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .interests-photos .interest-photo {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .interest-photo img {
    width: min(100%, 420px);
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .interest-photo figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .contact {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .contact-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .contact-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 2.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    transition:
      background-color var(--transition-normal),
      border-color var(--transition-normal),
      color var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .contact-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    border-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .contact-button.secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .contact-button.secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-background-alt);
    border-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    color: var(--color-primary-hover);
  }

  .skills-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: fit-content;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
  }

  .skills-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
